Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.72,0:02:01.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等我，希利斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.29,0:02:04.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希利斯   希利斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.70,0:02:07.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别这样，波里森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.93,0:02:11.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都一样很累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.17,0:02:13.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可不可以不要吵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.67,0:02:19.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下吧  但是·
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.04,0:02:22.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们和亚喜拉的距离应拉近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.41,0:02:24.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.22,0:02:29.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们也不全是军人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.26,0:02:32.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果太累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.69,0:02:34.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到时可能会输给亚喜拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.73,0:02:39.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你讲得对，大家休息一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.60,0:02:50.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死…终於受感动的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.51,0:02:57.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.12,0:03:03.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森为什么突然恢复感觉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.46,0:03:08.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知，我觉得以前的他比较成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.49,0:03:11.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他很久没有感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.63,0:03:14.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但现在突然有感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.77,0:03:15.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不知所措
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.57,0:03:19.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…希利斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.97,0:03:23.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母你帮一下他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.81,0:03:25.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去他不能在战场上立足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.01,0:03:28.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是希利斯，打仗是很可怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.45,0:03:31.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你又为什么要跟着我们来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.48,0:03:33.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我喜欢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.39,0:03:38.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么突然这样讲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.59,0:03:42.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没骗你，在被愤怒精灵控制时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.60,0:03:46.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在心底某处就产生了爱意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.70,0:03:50.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我可以很明确的讲出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.10,0:03:55.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森你可不可以告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.67,0:03:57.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会突然恢复感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.41,0:04:00.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是那个时候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.15,0:04:04.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在与亚喜拉打斗时被魔剑砍中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.38,0:04:08.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而那魔剑的力量溶进我身体里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.02,0:04:15.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那愤怒精灵就更加变弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.20,0:04:23.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是那时开始恢复的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.64,0:04:28.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此，亚喜拉的剑和龙的气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.71,0:04:31.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以有力量直接控制精灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.18,0:04:34.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是那愤怒精灵现在呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.61,0:04:37.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从波里森身体中逃走了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.85,0:04:39.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，还在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.55,0:04:43.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但它已经没力量控制我的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.69,0:04:49.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只我，别人也许都有愤怒精灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.83,0:04:52.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要拥有能控制它的理性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.93,0:04:54.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以不用怕它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.10,0:04:58.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森，恭喜你恢复感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.47,0:05:00.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我要先讲明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.54,0:05:03.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢的人是帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.24,0:05:05.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希利斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.41,0:05:07.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希利斯，不是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.95,0:05:11.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不知道什么是爱情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.45,0:05:13.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是把
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.25,0:05:16.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,输给帕母的感觉当成爱情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.82,0:05:20.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在输给亚喜拉的女战士时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.03,0:05:22.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也很生气的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.56,0:05:27.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和那女战士比起来还差很远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.07,0:05:30.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但输给中意的男人就觉得算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.21,0:05:38.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恢复感觉之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.91,0:05:40.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可以看透人心吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.98,0:05:44.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑，你了解我什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.48,0:05:47.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是真的爱帕母的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.25,0:05:49.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别把恨那女战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.12,0:05:51.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的感觉混为一谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.99,0:05:53.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，我讲得太过份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.28,0:06:13.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚喜拉大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.48,0:06:18.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会错，这就是入口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.75,0:06:20.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.22,0:06:22.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请等等，亚喜拉大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.59,0:06:26.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.39,0:06:31.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,煞星龙过几日一定会出去找食物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.00,0:06:34.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们就趁它不在的时候进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.37,0:06:38.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後就可以马上拿走支配的王锡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.57,0:06:43.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他讲得对，和饿肚子的龙战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.04,0:06:47.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我们不利，也很危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.85,0:06:49.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不认为会那么顺利完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.75,0:06:52.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古娄达，史枚蒂 你们在这里看守
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.25,0:06:56.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他人就等那家伙离开巢穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.05,0:07:26.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.25,0:07:27.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.92,0:07:30.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔龙煞星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.82,0:07:32.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是莱登的方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.93,0:07:35.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.36,0:07:39.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.63,0:07:42.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.90,0:07:44.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你讲是夫雷国的军队!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.77,0:07:47.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要改变计画
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.04,0:07:51.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以，而且煞星已经离巢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.81,0:07:53.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不可以放弃这个机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.21,0:07:55.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是·
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.31,0:07:57.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙就交给我们处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.62,0:08:00.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚喜拉大人请往龙口里去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.02,0:08:04.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿到支配的王锡  当罗德岛的王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.86,0:08:07.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真会讲话，古娄达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.56,0:08:10.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了，剩下的就拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.76,0:08:15.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.24,0:08:23.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来他们好像不让我们进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.94,0:08:25.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正想这样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.64,0:08:28.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为是谁，原来是之前那些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.71,0:08:30.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是有几个没见过面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.62,0:08:34.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个吟游诗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.79,0:08:37.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看着，波里森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.59,0:08:40.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会证明比那女人厉害给你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.43,0:08:44.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行的希利斯，你爬山已经很累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.50,0:08:46.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在跟她打，不可能会赢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.63,0:08:51.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题，那种人一下子就解决了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.24,0:08:53.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希利斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.44,0:09:00.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪，不见亚喜拉的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.28,0:09:02.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.92,0:09:07.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你们去找亚喜拉大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.19,0:09:10.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧，我的骷髅士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.31,0:09:28.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骷髅兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.04,0:09:30.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，不见亚喜拉的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.08,0:09:33.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一定是在洞里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在煞星龙不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.65,0:09:37.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想趁机去拿支配的王锡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.52,0:09:40.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了，这里就交给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.45,0:09:42.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请陛下先走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.72,0:09:44.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.79,0:09:47.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.90,0:09:54.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别让他进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.37,0:09:58.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.41,0:10:03.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.51,0:10:08.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗神法拉尼斯，请赐我力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.65,0:10:12.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请赐我石的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.96,0:10:24.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛发，请让这人恢复过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.46,0:10:27.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来那女人是玛发的祭师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.14,0:10:32.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么，是地震吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.24,0:10:41.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好!是大地之神威尼斯精灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.48,0:10:48.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我风之王希鲁非
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.23,0:10:59.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.35,0:11:15.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一次又一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.92,0:11:25.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那女人到哪里去，应该在这附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.99,0:11:27.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行的希利斯，你打不过的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.19,0:11:29.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.73,0:11:35.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危险，希利斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.60,0:11:39.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.28,0:11:53.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终於找到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.92,0:11:57.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为是谁，原来是之前的小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.46,0:12:00.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又想决战了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.69,0:12:03.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前是我太大意，但这次不同了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.26,0:12:08.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大意!应该是讲实力之差吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.13,0:12:10.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.44,0:12:18.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行的，希利斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.36,0:12:36.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个贺而夫想不到会使用风神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.93,0:12:38.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样真是势均力敌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.66,0:12:43.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你要对帕母不利的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.90,0:12:47.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会杀掉你，你没选择了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.18,0:13:01.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他真厉害，看来我要学习剑法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.82,0:13:05.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到夫雷国有这样的魔术师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.13,0:13:15.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.74,0:13:22.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不可以死在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.71,0:13:31.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请搬迁精灵把我送走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.15,0:13:37.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被逃脱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.72,0:13:38.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.42,0:13:41.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来是我错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.43,0:13:45.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不应该教你魔术  应该教做战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.07,0:13:51.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了小女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.70,0:13:53.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动作比之前还要迟钝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.77,0:13:56.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要吵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.58,0:14:08.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能输，我不可以输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.96,0:14:16.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了，你刚才的魄力全不见了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.73,0:14:22.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暗黑之王  请赐我黑暗力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.07,0:14:30.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大地之母玛发  全靠你的名解放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然可以挡住我的魔法，既然...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.01,0:14:38.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.99,0:14:42.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.65,0:14:45.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻莫请将这男人的灵魂取走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.56,0:14:53.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暗黑之王  请将她讲的话毁灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.13,0:14:57.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把她的话全变成相反...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.97,0:15:01.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛发，请让这人永远的沉睡
